import React from 'react'
import {
  List,
  Datagrid,
  TextField,
  DateField,
  EditButton,
  DeleteButton,
  UrlField,
  
} from 'react-admin'

const SongList = (props) => {
  return (
    <List {...props}>
      <Datagrid>
        <TextField source='id' />
        <TextField source='song_name' />
        <TextField source='song_duration' />
        <DateField source='date_added' />  
        <TextField source='stream_count' label='Stream Count'/>
        <TextField source="files.rawFile.path"  label='Path' style={{}}/>  
        <UrlField target="_blank" source="song_image" />
        <TextField source='adder_user-id' label="adder_user-id" />  
        <EditButton basePath='/songs' />
        <DeleteButton basePath='/songs' />
      </Datagrid>
    </List>
  )
}

export default SongList
